117
00:06:36,219 --> 00:06:38,450
Jika kalian pulang larut, jangan datang.

118
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:40,649
Tidur saja di luar. Paham?

119
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:45,589
Semua setuju, bukan?

120
00:06:45,589 --> 00:06:46,630
Lanjut.

