159
00:08:39,709 --> 00:08:41,009
Joon Soo.

160
00:08:42,209 --> 00:08:43,979
Minumlah.

161
00:08:45,249 --> 00:08:46,749
Aku tidak punya seloki.

162
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:06,469
