176
00:10:11,329 --> 00:10:12,969
Omong-omong, Anda tidak perlu terlalu formal kepadaku.

177
00:10:12,969 --> 00:10:16,400
Toh, kita akan selalu bertemu di rumah ini.

178
00:10:17,770 --> 00:10:18,770
Begitukah?

179
00:10:21,609 --> 00:10:22,640
Pak Yoo.

180
00:10:23,509 --> 00:10:24,749
